data.description: This attached three-bedroom, two-bathroom villa in Alexandra at World Tennis Club is almost 1,600 square feet under air and seems like a single-family home! The layout includes a laundry room, an entry lobby, and high ceilings in the living, dining, and eat-in kitchen areas. Storm shutters and a screened lanai for convenience. Fitting a king-sized bed, the roomy master bedroom opens to an en suite bathroom including separate shower and soaking tub, as well as a sizable walk-in closet. All facilities, including lawn care and cable TV, are covered by HOA dues! This property is perfectly situated south of Pine Ridge Rd, close to the airport, Mercato, Waterside Shops, 5th Ave, Gulf beaches, and highly regarded schools. Accessible by foot or bicycle to a supermarket, pharmacy, and bank
